to your brain forgetting it.

175
00:12:27,690 --> 00:12:31,490
But what if
you can't forget anything?

176
00:12:32,389 --> 00:12:36,190
What if you're still reliving
the breakup even after 10 years?

177
00:12:36,429 --> 00:12:39,330
- That's terrible.
- Goodness.

178
00:12:39,330 --> 00:12:43,029
So you shouldn't blame your brain
for forgetting things.

179
00:12:43,799 --> 00:12:47,240
There's actually
a good side to that.

180
00:12:47,970 --> 00:12:49,710
