00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,009
(We thank Park Seong Keun,
Kim Seon Ho, Rowoon, and Yura...)

523
00:28:56,009 --> 00:28:57,109
(for their special appearances.)

524
00:29:10,990 --> 00:29:13,220
(Find Me in Your Memory)

525
00:29:13,220 --> 00:29:14,559
Hyperthymesia?

526
00:29:14,559 --> 00:29:16,359
Remembering too much is
a medical condition?

527
00:29:16,359 --> 00:29:17,990
It's not that I remember a lot.

528
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:20,029
I just can't forget anything.

529
00:29:20,029 --> 00:29:21,029
Are you going to die?

530
00:29:21,029 --> 00:29:22,970
Does your first love
look like me too?

531
00:29:22,970 --> 00:29:24,200
Wake up, Seo Yeon!

532
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:25,339
I'm sorry.

533
00:29:25,769 --> 00:29:28,000
I can't stop or end this.

534
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:30,339
It's as if I'm stuck in that memory.

535
00:29:30,470 --> 00:29:31,539
I love you.

536
00:29:31,670 --> 00:29:33,279
I'll remember this forever.

537
00:29:33,710 --> 00:29:36,079
Why did he look so sad?

538
00:29:36,210 --> 00:29:38,549
What was he saying in that silence?

539
00:29:38,579 --> 00:29:41,380
Jung Seo Yeon. Do you know her?
